## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of music's effects on human psychology. The studies referenced vary in their methodologies and sample sizes, which may affect the generalizability of the results. Additionally, individual differences in musical preference and cultural context can influence the impact of music, which may not be fully captured in the studies reviewed. Further research is needed to explore these variables and their implications.